Already installed cursor themes can be viewed with the command:

find /usr/share/icons ~/.local/share/icons ~/.icons -type d -name "cursors"

~/.icons/default/index.theme
[icon theme]
Inherits=Adwaita

ln -s /usr/share/icons/Adwaita/cursors/cursorr ~/.icons/default/cursors

[KDE - ArchWiki](https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/KDE#Plasma_cursor_sometimes_shown_incorrectly)
